sequenceDiagram
    participant S as Source/API/CSV/Google Trends
    participant Scraper as Scraper/Importer
    participant Raw as data/raw
    participant Norm as Normalizer
    participant DB as SQLite/PostgreSQL
    participant Proc as data/processed
    participant UI as Dashboard/API
    participant Report as Reports

    S->>Scraper: Fetch/import data
    Scraper->>Raw: Save raw artifact
    Scraper->>Norm: Normalize columns
    Norm->>DB: Upsert observations
    Norm->>Proc: Save processed CSV
    UI->>DB: Query observations
    UI->>Report: Generate PDF/TeX/XLSX/CSV
    Report->>Proc: Save report artifacts
